---
title: Japanese statistics day poster
---

<img src="/images/japanese-wsd-poster.jpg" alt="World Statistics Day 2015 poster in Japanese" style="width:300px"><br><br>20 October 2015 is the second World Statistics day.  But did you know that 18 October this year is also the Japanese Statistics Day?  To promote both celebrations, the government of Japan has released a poster featuring the image of the World Statistics Day 2015 logo and the Japanese translation of the slogan "Better data. Better lives."
